reviewText:
This is one of the more on-theme of the Toon Factory $1 DVDs as it does, indeed, feature girls we love. 8 of the 16 cartoons on this disk are Betty Boop shorts, including the color short "Poor Cinderella." The rest are a mix of Little Audrey and Little Lulu cartoons, with one Molly Moo-Cow thrown in for inter-species representation.

The 16 shorts in this collection are:
1) More Pep
2) Be Human
3) Baby Be Good
4) Betty Boop's Ker-Choo
5) Poor Cinderella
6) The Lost Dream
7) The Seapreme Court
8) Cad and Caddy
9) A Bout With a Trout
10) Betty Boop's Rise to Fame
11) Betty Boop's Crazy Inventions
12) Is My Palm Read
13) Molly Moo-Cow and the Butterflies
14) Bored of Education
15) Goofy Goofy Gander
16) Tarts and Flowers
